## üéØ PROJECT OVERVIEW (Technical)

**What we're building:** A web application that helps organizations plan, track, and achieve their carbon reduction goals. Users can organize emissions by Scope 1, 2, and 3 categories, create reduction tactics with timelines and costs, and visualize progress with interactive charts.

**Target users:** Sustainability managers and environmental consultants at organizations

**Key differentiator:** Privacy-first approach - username-only authentication (no email required), anonymous organization names

